<h3 class="date"><a href="/2010/mar/31/">&#x27a0;</a> March 31, 2010</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="turing-machine" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://aturingmachine.com/">A Turing Machine</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>I love, love, LOVE this. Someone has built a real-world turing machine which loads programs from an SD card, and uses a dry-erase pen to write on 35mm film leader. Gorgeous.</p>

